The area of triangle = 1/2 * base * height = 1/2 * (a+b) * y = 1/2 * (a+b) * (y/2) = 1/2 * (a+b) * y/2 = (a+b)/2 * y = (a+b)/2 * y = (a−b)/2y. So the answer is (e).

